&#x2F;* 播放按钮覆盖层 *&#x2F;.play-overlay &#123;  position: absolute;  top: 0;  left: 0;  width: 100%;  height: 100%;  display: flex;  align-items: center;  justify-content: center;  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);  border-radius: 50%;  opacity: 1;  transition: opacity 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;&#125;
